plot: When Sebastian and his two friends decide to play with Yancy, the neighborhood outcast, the day turns sour as Sebastian punches Yancy in the face. After a bad nightmare, Sebastian, now an adult finds Yancy to apologize.
title: Sexual Tyrannosaurus
